Study analyser

①

Use this SQL query to get the data in the correct format

SELECT jsonb_set( s."Data"::jsonb, '{CreatedAt}', to_jsonb(s."CreatedAt") ) as "NestedData" FROM "Studies" s LEFT JOIN "Projects" p ON p."Id" = s."ProjectId" LEFT JOIN "Accounts" a ON a."Id" = p."AccountId" WHERE s."ProjectId" IN ( SELECT p."Id" FROM "Projects" p LEFT JOIN "Accounts" a ON p."AccountId" = a."Id" WHERE a."Company" LIKE '%%' ) AND p."UserId" IN ( SELECT "Id" FROM "Users" u WHERE "Email" NOT LIKE '%dragonflyai.co%' ) AND s."Data" != '[]' AND s."CreatedAt" > NOW() - INTERVAL '6 months' LIMIT 100
